OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine in
OL,7,Fplaces. Then dry in the east
OL,8,Fovernight, but patchy rain spreading
OL,9,Fto the west. Freshening westerly
OL,10,Fbreeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FRather cloudy start with
OL,13,Fpatchy light rain in the west. Dry
OL,14,Fafternoon with some hazy sunshine
OL,15,Fdeveloping in the east. Brisk westerly
OL,16,Fwinds. Patchy rain spreading southeast
OL,17,Fin the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
