OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLight
OL,6,Frain spreading southeast Saturday
OL,7,Fmorning, drier for a time, then more
OL,8,Frain later. Breezy. Mostly dry Sunday,
OL,9,Fperhaps a few showers. Dry start
OL,10,FMonday, some rain in west later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
